      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 23,
      "message": "Already had this question, below is the answer:\n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/so/+/106096/2/adapters/mso-ve-vnfm-adapter/src/main/java/org/onap/so/adapters/vevnfm/util/NullOptional.java#23",
